Amalungu eNdlu yoWiso-mthetho yaseWales axhalabile ukuba aya kuthelekiswa neMuppets
Kukho ukuphazamiseka phakathi kwamalungu eNdlu yoWiso-mthetho yaseWales ngesigqibo sokutshintsha isihloko sawo sibe yiMWP (Member of the Welsh Parliament - Ilungu lePalamente yaseWales).
Esi siphakamiso siphuma kwizicwangciso zokutshintsha igama langoku elithi Welsh Assembly libe yi Welsh Parliament.
Amalungu eNdlu yoWiso-mthetho yamaqela ezopolitiko axhalabile ukuba igama elitsha libonakala lihleka.
Elinye ilungu leNdibano yeZwelonke yaseWales leqela leLabour lathi i-MWP iqhotyoshelwe yi-TWP ne-Pwp.
Kubafundi abangaphandle kweWales: twp sisiWelsh kuthetha isiyatha kwaye pwp sisiWelsh kuthetha isifo.
Elinye ilungu leNdibano yeZwelonke yaseWales lePlaid Party lathi iqela liphela alivuyiswa kwaye licebise iindlela ezongezelelweyo.
Elinye ilungu leqela laseWelsh Conservative Party lathi iqela lalo livulelekile ukutshintsha igama, kodwa laqaphela ukuba amagama athi MWP noMuppet afana kakhulu.
Kule meko, oonobumba baseWelsh abathi W bavakaliswe njenge-u emfutshane.
IKomishoni yeNdibano yeZwelonke yaseWales, ekwangoku esebenza ekuqulunqeni imithetho yokuphumeza utshintsho lwamabizo, yathi: Kwakungamalungu eNdibano yeZwelonke yaseWales ngokwawo athatha isigqibo sokugqibela kwisihloko sabo esitsha.
UMthetho kaRhulumente waseWales ka-2017 wanika amalungu eNdlu yoWiso-mthetho yaseWales ilungelo lokutshintsha igama leNdlu.
NgoJuni, iKomishoni yapapasha iziphumo zophando olwenziwa esidlangalaleni ngeziphakamiso, nto leyo eyabonisa ukuba abantu abaninzi bavakalelwa kukuba iNdibano yeZwelonke kufuneka ibizwe ngokuba yiPalamente.
Ngokuphathelele isihloko samalungu eNdlu yoWiso-mthetho, iKomishoni yacela ukuba kubekho iiWelsh Parliament Members okanye iiWMPs, kodwa ukhetho lweMWP lwafumana inkxaso enkulu kwiingxoxo zikawonkewonke.
Okwangoku amalungu eNdlu yoWiso-mthetho aza kucebisa ngeendlela ezongezelelweyo, kodwa uMongameli uElin Jones uza kuba nobunzima bokufikelela kwisivumelwano.
Umthetho weziNguqu uquka nezinye izilungiso kwindlela esebenza ngayo iNdlu yoWiso-mthetho, kuquka imithetho esusa amalungu eNdlu yoWiso-mthetho kunye nolwakhiwo lwenkqubo yeekomiti.
Amalungu eNdlu yoWiso-mthetho aya kuba nakho ukuvota ngokusisigxina kwisihloko sawo esitsha xa exoxa ngomthetho.
