ISainsbury's ifuna ukufikelela kwimarike yaseBritani
ISainsbury's ikhuphisana neBoots, iSuperdrug neDebenhams ize iseke amacandelo obuhle apho kusebenza khona amagosa agcisa, njengakwindawo yempahla enkulu.
Eli phulo liyinxalenye yesicwangciso sokubamba imarike yobuhle yase-UK, enexabiso le-Â£2.8 yezigidigidi, kwaye iyaqhubeka ikhula, njengoko ukuthengiswa kwefashoni kunye nezinto zendlu kuqhubeka ukwehla. Amacandelo amakhulu obuhle aya kuvavanywa kwiivenkile ezili-11 kwilizwe liphela. Ukuba ayaphumelela, aya kufakwa kwiivenkile ezininzi kunyaka ozayo.
Ukutshalwa kwemali kwimarike yobuhle kukwakubangelwa kukuba iivenkile ezinkulu zifuna ukuzalisa iilekese ezazikade zikho iiTV, ii-microphone nezinto zangaphakathi ngemveliso eyahlukileyo.
ISainsbury's ifuna ukuphinda kabini ubuhle bayo, ize inikeze iimveliso ezingama-3 000, kuquka ne-Revlon, u-Essie, u-Twizerman noGqirha PawPaw.
Kwakhona, uluhlu olukhoyo lweL'Oreal, iMaybelline neBurt's Bees luza kuba nendawo engakumbi, kunye nendawo yokubonisa ngemveliso nganye, njengakwisitolo esinjengeBoots.
