Ukongezelela, iFragrance Shop iza kuhlolisisa izilungiselelo kwiivenkile ezimbini zaseSainsbury's.
Njengoko abantu abaninzi bethenga kwi-intanethi yaye bethenga ukutya okuncinane kwiindawo zokuthenga izidlo ezikhulu mihla le, iivenkile ezinkulu kufuneka zisebenze nzima ukuze zikhuthaze abantu ukuba bathenge kuzo.
UMike Coupe, umphathi omkhulu waseSainsbury's, uthi iivenkile ziya kuqhubeka zibonakala njengeendawo zokuthengisa, njengoko iivenkile ezinkulu zisabela kwiivenkile ezisezantsi zeAldi neLidl, ezinemisebenzi emininzi kunye nezingenanto yokutya.
I-Sainsbury's iye yahlanganisa iindawo ezithengiswayo ze-Argos kumakhulu eenkampani, yavula neendawo zokuhlala ezininzi ukususela ekuthengeni zombini ezi ngxekweni kwiminyaka emibini edluleyo.
Ixesha elidlulileyo xa ivenkile enkulu yayizama ukuguqula amacandelo ayo obuhle neekhemesti, yaphumelela.
Ngo-2000 iSainsbury's yazama ukusebenzisana neBoots, kodwa le ntsebenziswano yaphela xa kwavela ingxabano malunga nokwabelana ngenzuzo evela kwicandelo leekhemesti kwiivenkile ezinkulu.
Eli qhinga litsha ukususela oko iSainsbury's yathengisa iivenkile zayo ezingama-281 kwiivenkile zayo kwiminyaka emithathu edluleyo nge-125 yezigidi zeengqekembe zeBritane kuCelesio, ongumnini womxokelelwane weLloyds Pharmacy.
I-Lloyds nayo yayiza kuba nendima kule nkqubo, ngokongeza uluhlu olubanzi lweempawu zokunyamekela isikhumba, kuquka iLa Roche-Posay neVichy, kwiivenkile ezine.
UPaul Mills-Hicks, umphathi wezentengiso eSainsbury's, wathi: "Sitshintshe ngokupheleleyo indlela esiyilungisa ngayo indawo yethu yobuhle ukuze ibe mnandi ngakumbi kubathengi bethu.
Siye safaka imali kuqeqesho olukhethekileyo lwabasebenzi bethu, abaya kuba ngabacebisi.
Ngenxa yemveliso yethu, sinika wonke umntu into ayifunayo, yaye ngenxa yendawo ekhangayo neendawo ezifanelekileyo, siqinisekisa ukuba abathengi bethu bayakuthanda ukuthenga izinto zabo zobuhle kuthi, kungekhona ngendlela yakudala.
