Umfanekiso kaCromwell kwiPalamente yaseBritani ngowona mva nje wahlushwa 'ngumlo wokubhala imbali'
Ukugxothwa kwalo mfanekiso-ngqangi kwakuya kuba sisiqinisekiso esingombongo sokutshatyalaliswa kwamaTaliban kwezinto ezininzi zobugcisa zenkcubeko nezonqulo ezenziwa ngabalandeli bakhe abazinikeleyo abangamaPuritan.
Kodwa iCromwell Society yathi le nto yayithethwa nguCrick yayisisicaphukiso nesenzelwa ukuzama ukubuyisela imbali.
UJohn Goldsmith, umongameli weCromwell Society, wathi: "Kwakungenakuphepheka ukuba ingxoxo yangoku yokususwa kwemifanekiso eqingqiweyo yayiza kubangela ukuba umfanekiso kaOliver Cromwell ubethwe phandle nje kweeNdlu zePalamente.
I-iconoclasm yeMfazwe YesiNgesi ayizange ilawulwe okanye yenziwe nguCromwell.
Mhlawumbi uCromwell ongalunganga wayeza kunikelwa ngenxa yezenzo zomkhulu wakhe uThomas kwinkulungwane edluleyo.
Lo mfanekiso ubalaseleyo kaCromwell, owenziwe nguSir William Hamo Thorneycroft, ungqina ukuba abantu babecinga ntoni ngenkulungwane ye-19 yaye ungunxalenye yokubhala imbali yomntu abaninzi abathi usafuna ukuhlonitshwa.
UGoldsmith wathi kwiThe Sunday Telegraph: "UCromwell uthathwa ngabaninzi, mhlawumbi ngakumbi ekupheleni kwenkulungwane ye-19 kunangoku, njengomkhuseli wepalamente kwingcinezelo yangaphandle, kwimeko yakhe ngokuqinisekileyo iyinkosi.
Ukuba le ngcamango ichanile kusini na, kusekho impikiswano.
Kodwa ke into eqinisekileyo kukuba, umlo owawuphakathi kwenkulungwane ye-17 wavelisa inkqubela phambili yesizwe sethu, yaye uCromwell ungumntu owaziwayo owenza elinye icala laloo mgama.
Kwakhona, izinto awazenzayo njengoMkhuseli weNkosi zifanele ziqhayiswe kwaye zikhunjulwe.
Ingulube Eyayizidla Ngokubulala Yabulala Umlimi WaseTshayina
Ngokutsho kweendaba zasekuhlaleni, umfama othile wahlaselwa waza wabulawa yingulube kwintengiso ekumzantsi-ntshona weTshayina.
Le ndoda, eyaziwa ngegama likaYuan kuphela, yafunyanwa ifile kwisitulo sentengiso eLiupanshui, kwiphondo laseGuizhou, inesifo somoya esichukumisayo, yaye igcwele igazi, yatsho njalo iSouth China Morning Post ngeCawa.
Umfuyi wehagu ulungiselela ukufaka iihagu kwibhotwe lehagu, ngoMeyi 30, 2005, eXining, kwiphondo laseQinghai, eTshayina.
Kubikwa ukuba ngoLwesithathu, yena nomtshana wakhe babehamba besuka kwiphondo elingummelwane laseYunnan besiya kuthengisa iihagu ezili-15 kwimarike.
Ngentsasa elandelayo umtshana wakhe wamfumana efile, waza wafumanisa ukuba umnyango wehagu elumelwaneni uvulekile.
Umtshana wakhe uthi kwakukho ingulube enkulu enegazi emlonyeni wayo.
Ingxelo ithi, uphando lwezomthetho lubonisa ukuba le ngulube yayinesisindo esimalunga ne-250 kg yayimbulale umfama.
"Iimilenze yomtshana wam zazinesiphene esopha igazi", watsho umtshana ogama linguWu, ngokutsho kweGuiyang Evening News.
Kwiikhamera zokulinda, uYuan wafika kwimarike ngoLwesine ngo-4.40 ekuseni ukuze ondle iihagu zakhe.
Umzimba wakhe wafunyanwa malunga neyure kamva.
Isilwanyana esabulala loo mntu sasingeyomntu kaYuan okanye umtshana wakhe.
Igosa lentengiso laxelela i-Evening News ukuba le ngulube yayibekwe phantsi ukuze ingahlaseli abanye ngoxa amapolisa ayeqokelela ubungqina kuloo ndawo.
Kusithiwa intsapho kaYuan neenkampani ezilawula imarike zikwindawo ethetha ngayo ngokuhlawula ukufa kwakhe.
Oku akwenzeki rhoqo, kodwa kuye kwenzeka ngaphambili ukuba iihagu zibulale abantu.
Ngo-2016, ingulube yahlasela umfazi nomyeni wakhe kwifama yabo eMassachusetts, yaza loo ndoda yaguquka kakhulu.
Kwiminyaka elishumi ngaphambili, ingulube enobunzima obungama-300 kg yaxhaphaza umfama waseWales kwatrektara yakhe de umfazi wakhe wayigxotha.
Xa umfama othile waseOregon wadliwa ziingulube zakhe ngo-2012, umfama othile waseManitoba wavuma kwiCBC News ukuba iingulube aziqhelekanga ukuba zibe nogonyamelo, kodwa ukuba ukunambitheka kwegazi kunokubangela ukuba zibe nogonyamelo.
Zizinto nje zokudlala.
Bafana nabantwana, banomdla kakhulu. Abafuni kwenzakalisa abantu.
Wathi, "Umele ubahlonele".
Umsila wonyango uRosa uzisa imvula eninzi kumzantsi-ntshona weUnited States
Njengoko kwakuprofetiwe, iNkanyamba uRosa iya kuncipha njengoko ifikelela kumanzi abandayo kunxweme olusemantla eMexico.
Noko ke, kwiintsuku ezizayo, uRosa uza kuzisa imvula eninzi kumantla naseMexico.
URosa, owawuneemitha eziyi-135 ngeyure, waba sisiphango esibizwa ngokuba yiCategory 1 ngentsimbi yesihlanu ekuseni ngeCawa, ibe yayikude ngeekhilomitha eziyi-620 ukusuka ePunta Eugenia, eMexico.
Kulindeleke ukuba uRosa athabathe inyathelo elingasentla ngeCawa.
Ngelo xesha, umlambo uqalisa ukwakha phezu kwePacific Ocean, ohambela ngasempuma ukuya kunxweme olusentshona yeUnited States. NgoMvulo, xa uRosa esondela kwiNhlonhlo yaseBaja California njengesiphepho esishushu, ukufuma kwezona ndawo zishushu kuya kunyuka uye emantla, kumzantsi-ntshona weUnited States.
URosa uza kuzisa imvula ye-10 cm kwiindawo ezithile zaseMexico ngoMvulo.
Emva koko, ukufuma kwelitye elishushu okuphendula imvula eshushu ezayo kuya kubangela imvula eninzi kumazantsi-ntshona kwimihla ezayo.
Kwindawo ethile, imvula enobubanzi obuphakathi kwe-2 ne-10 cm iza kubangela izikhukula eziyingozi, imingxuma kunye nokududuma komhlaba entlango.
Amanzi asezindaweni ezishushu aya kubangela imvula engamasentimitha amahlanu ukuya kwamashumi asibhozo ngeyure, ingakumbi kumacandelo asezantsi eNevada naseArizona.
Kukho imvula enokuba ziisentimitha eziyi-5 ukuya kweziyi-10 kwiindawo ezisezantsi-ntshona, ingakumbi kummandla omkhulu waseArizona.
Kukho izikhukula eziqhushumbayo ezinobungozi obukhulu ngenxa yokuba imvula yelitye elishushu inokuwela ngokubanzi.
Kunconywa kakhulu ukuba ungene entlango unyawo xa kusongelwa yimvula.
Imvula eninzi inokujika imingxuma ibe yimilambo enomsindo, yaye isiphepho siya kuvelisa imimoya nentaba-mbi.
Iinkanyamba ezikufutshane zisa imvula eninzi kwiindawo eziselunxwemeni loMzantsi California.
Kukho imvula enokuba ziisentimitha eziyi-1,5 ezinokubangela imingxuma encinane neendlela ezicothayo.
Oku kuya kuba yimvula yokuqala yexesha lemvula kweli lizwe.
Imvula ehlaziyiweyo yaseArizona iza kusondela ngeCawa ebusuku de kube kusasa ngoMvulo, ize imvula isasazeke ngakumbi ngoMvulo emva kwemini nangeLwesibini.
Imvula eninzi iza kutsala iCawa kwiiFour Corners ize iqhubeke de kube ngoLwesithathu.
Ngo-Oktobha, amaqondo obushushu aseMerika anokuzamazama ngamandla kuba i-Arctic iya kubanda, kodwa amaqondo obushushu asezindaweni ezishushu aya kuhlala eshushu.
Maxa wambi, oko kukhokelela kumahluko omkhulu wobushushu kumgama omfutshane.
Kukho umzekelo omhle wokutshintsha kwamaqondo obushushu okuphawulekayo kumbindi weUnited States ngeCawa.
Umahluko obandayo phakathi kweKansas City, eMissouri, neOmaha, eNebraska, neSt. Louis neDes Moines, eIowa, phantse ziidigri ezingama-20.
Kwiintsuku ezizayo, ubushushu obuhlala buhleli behlobo buza kuzama ukwakha nokwandisa kwakhona.
Kwiindawo ezininzi zaseMntla naseMpuma yeUnited States, uOktobha kulindeleke ukuba aqalise ukufudumala, yaye amaqondo obushushu aya kuthi afike kuma-30Â°C, ukususela kumathafa asezantsi ukuya kumacandelo aseMntla-mpuma.
ENew York, ngoLwesibini, ingama-27 degrees, nto leyo ebangela ukuba ubushushu bube ngama-10 degrees ngaphezu komlinganiselo.
Izibikezelo zethu zemozulu zexesha elide zibonisa ukuba kuya kubakho amaqondo obushushu angaphezulu komlinganiselo kwimpuma yeUnited States de kube phakathi ku-Oktobha.
Abantu abangaphezu kwezigidi ezingama-20 babukele umsitho kaBrett Kavanaugh
Abantu abangaphezu kwezigidi ezingama-20 babukele enye yeenkqubo ezintandathu zikamabonwakude ngoLwesine, bebukele ubungqina obuchukumisayo bukaBrett Kavanaugh, umviwa weNkundla Ephakamileyo yaseMerika, noChristine Blasey Ford, ibhinqa elalimtyhola ngokumhlasela okuxelwa ukuba kwenzeka kwiminyaka yoo-1980.
Okwangoku, umngcipheko wezopolitiko waqhubeka, ngoxa iinkqubo zenkqubo zothutho lweendaba zazisenza kube nzima ukuqhubeka nokuvavanya isimangalo sangoLwesihlanu: isivumelwano esasilungiselelwe nguJeff Flake, usenyuli waseArizona, ukuze aphande ityala kangangeveki.
UFord uxelele iKomiti yezoBulungisa yeSenate ukuba uqinisekile nge-100% ukuba umntu onxilile uKavanaugh wamchukumisa waza wazama ukumkhulula kwiqela lesikolo samabanga aphakamileyo.
UKavanaugh wathi ebunquleni bakhe, wayeqinisekile nge-100% ukuba oku akenzekanga.
Kubonakala ngathi abantu abangaphezu kwezigidi ezingama-20.4 abaxelwe nguNilsen ngoLwesihlanu babukele.
Le nkampani yabala inani eliphakathi labalandeli kwiCBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel neMSNBC.
Iinkcukacha-manani zazingafumaneki ngoko nangoko kwezinye iinethiwekhi ezasasaza ityala, njengePBS, C-SPAN neFox Business Network.
Yaye uNielsen udla ngokuba nobunzima bokubala abantu abajonga iofisi.
Xa kuthelekiswa noko, oko kufana nokudlala umdlalo webhola ekhatywayo okanye ukuphumelela iOscars.
I-Fox News Channel, exhasa ngokupheleleyo ukuqeshwa kukaKavanaugh, yayinababukeli abaninzi ngosuku lokuvalelwa kwecala: ngokwesilinganiso, izibukeli ezizizigidi ezingama-5.69, ngokutsho kukaNielsen.
I-ABC ilandele ngezigidi ezingama-3.26 zabukeli.
I-CBS yayinababukeli abazizigidi eziyi-3.1, i-NBC yayinababukeli abazizigidi eziyi-2.94, i-MSNBC yayinababukeli abazizigidi eziyi-2.89 yaye i-CNN yayinababukeli abazizigidi eziyi-2.52 ngokutsho kukaNielsen.
Emva kokuvalelwa kweembambano, abantu baqhubeka benomdla.
UFlake wayengumntu obalulekileyo kwinto eyenzeka ngoLwesihlanu.
Emva kokuba iofisi yaloo mntu ulawulayo iGumrhu Elilawulayo likhuphe isaziso sokuba uza kuxhasa uKavanaugh ngelizwi lakhe, iinkqubo ze-CNN ne-CBS ngoLwesihlanu ekuseni zafaka ingxelo yokuba ababhikishi bamemeza xa wayezama ukuthatha ikheshi ukuya kwiNtlanganiso yeKomiti yezoBulungisa.
Waqhubeka emi imizuzu embalwa ebukele phantsi ngoxa wayethukwa, ephila kwi-CNN.
"Ndilapha phambi kwakho", watsho omnye umfazi.
Ngaba ucinga ukuba uxelela abantu inyaniso?
Omnye wathi: "Unamandla, kodwa abafazi abaninzi abanamandla".
UFlake wathi iofisi yakhe ikhuphe ingxelo, yaye ngaphambi nje kokuba ivale i-elevator, wongezelela ukuba uza kuthetha okungakumbi ebudeni bentlanganiso.
Iinkqubo ezahlukahlukeneyo zenza ukuba yonke into ibekho xa iKomiti yezoBulungisa yacela ukuba kuvotelwe ukubekwa kukaKavanaugh kwiSenate kwiiyure ezimbalwa kamva.
Kodwa uFlake wathi uza kuvuma kuphela ukuba i-FBI iza kuphonononga izityholo ezibhekiswe kumntu okhethiweyo kwiveki ezayo, nto leyo iDemocrats abanyanzelisayo.
UFlake wancedwa ngumhlobo wakhe uChris Coons, owayengumSetyhini weSizwe, owayengumDemokhrasi.
UFlake wenza isigqibo sakhe emva kokubonisana noCoons kunye neenkokeli ezininzi zeSizwe.
Ukhetho lukaFlake lwalubalulekile kuba kwakubonakala ukuba amaRiphabliki awayi kuba namavoti afunekayo ukuze avume uKavanaugh ngaphandle kophando.
UMongameli Trump uye wavula uphando lwe-FBI malunga nezityholo ezenziwa kuKavanaugh.
UNdunankulu waseBritani uMay utyhola abagxeki 'bokuba ngumdlalo wezopolitiko' weBrexit
Kwi-interview ne-Sunday Times, uMongameli u-Theresa May watyhola abezopolitiko ababekugxeka ukuphuma kwakhe kwi-European Union ngokuthi 'ngumdlalo wezopolitiko' ngekamva laseBritani nokugxotha iminqweno yesizwe.
UMongameli waseBritani uTheresa May uza kufika kwiNgqungquthela yeConservative Party eBirmingham, e-UK, nge-29 kaSeptemba 2018.
Kwinto enye, kwiphepha elifanayo lephephandaba, owayesakuba nguMphathiswa Wezangaphandle uBoris Johnson wagxininisa ukuhlasela kwakhe oko kwakuthiwa yiCherquers Plan for Brexit, esithi isiphakamiso sakhe sokuba iBritani ne-EU ziqokelelane iirhafu zokubala kwakubonisa ukuba akufanelekanga.
Ukudubula kukaWayde Sims: Amapolisa abamba uDyteon Simpson esityholwa ngokufa komdlali weLSU
Amapolisa abambe umntu osolwayo ngenxa yokudubula uWayde Sims, umdlali webhola ekhatywayo waseLSU oneminyaka engama-20 ubudala, ebulawa.
UDyteon Simpson, oneminyaka engama-20 ubudala, ubanjwe waza wavalelwa entolongweni ngenxa yokubulala, utshilo amapolisa aseBaton Rouge.
Abasemagunyeni bakhupha ividiyo yomlo owaba phakathi kukaSims noSimsons, yaye amapolisa athi uSims walahlekelwa ziiglasi zakhe xa wayesilwa.
Amapolisa afumana iiglasi kwindawo eyayisenziwa ngayo le nto, aza afumana iDNA kaSimpson kwiiglasi, itsho njalo iWAFB, isikhululo seTV seCBS.
Amapolisa ambuza uSimpson, aze kamva athi wayevuma ukuba wadutshulwa waza wafa.
Ummeli ubhala ukuba imali yakhe ibekwe kwi-350,000 yeedola.
Umhloli wezidumbu wephondo laseMpuma Baton Rouge, ngoLwesihlanu, wapapasha ingxelo yesigqibo esithi isizathu sokufa sisifo esisifo esisifo esisifo esisifo esithe sabulala abantu abaninzi.
Le ngxelo ithi iFugitive Task Force yeLouisiana State Police, iCrime Lab yePolisa laseLizania, iSouthern University Police kunye nabemi basekuhlaleni bonke bancedisa kuphando olukhokelela ekubanjweni.
UMlawuli wezemidlalo waseLSU uJoe Alleva, wabulela amapolisa asekuhlaleni ngomsebenzi wawo wokusebenzela nokulwela ubulungisa.
USims wayeneminyaka engama-20 ubudala.
Wayenemitha eyi-180 yaye wakhulela eBaton Rouge, apho uyise, uWayne, wayedlala khona ibhola ekhatywayo kwi-LSU.
Kulo nyaka uphelileyo, wayeqengqeleka amanqaku ayi-5.6 nama-2.6 eengqungquthela.
NgoLwesihlanu ekuseni, uWill Wade, umqeqeshi webhola ekhatywayo weLSU wathi iqela liphelelwe lixesha yaye libuhlungu ngenxa yokufa kukaWaydes.
"Le yimeko osoloko unethemba lokuba ayiyi kwenzeka", utsho uWade.
Iintaba-mlilo Zithulula Umlotha KwiMexico City
Umlotha owatyhilwa yintaba-mlilo iPopocatepetl uye wafikelela kummandla osemazantsi kwedolophu elikomkhulu laseMexico.
IZiko leZizwe lokuThintelwa kweNtlekele lalumkisa abantu baseMexico ukuba bahlale kude nentaba-mlilo ngoMgqibelo ophelileyo, emva kokuba umsebenzi we-crater uqhube kwaye kwafunyanwa imveliso yegesi ne-asphalt engama-183 ngexesha leeyure ezingama-24.
Iziko labona ukubila nokuduma kaninzi.
Kwiinethiwekhi zentlalo, kuye kwavela imifanekiso yomlotha omncinane kwiindlela zeemoto kwiindawo ezikufutshane nesixeko saseMexico, njengeXochimilco.
I-Geophysicists ibone ukunyuka komsebenzi kwintaba-mlilo, ekumgama weekhilomitha ezingama-72 kumazantsi-mpuma kwikomkhulu, okokuqala ukususela ngoSeptemba 2017, xa inyikima enamandla angama-7.1 izinyikima eMexico.
Le ntaba-mlilo ibizwa ngokuba yiDon Goyo yaye isebenza ukususela ngo-1994.
