INkanyamba URosa isongela iPhoenix, eLas Vegas, eSalt Lake City ngamanzi amaninzi (anokuchaphazela iindawo ezomileyo)
Kunqabile ukuba kubekho uxinzelelo lweemvula ezishushu oluya kufikelela eArizona, kodwa oku kuya kwenzeka kanye kanye ekuqaleni kweveki ezayo, kuba amandla ashiywe yiRosa aya kutshintsha aye kumazantsi ntshona entlango, nto leyo ebangela ukuba kubekho izikhukula.
I-National Weather Service iye yanika izilumkiso zamanzi ezikhukula ngokukhawuleza ngoMvulo nangoLwesibini entshona yeArizona ukuya kutsho emzantsi nasempuma yeNevada, nakumazantsi mpuma eCalifornia naseUtah, kuquka izixeko zasePhoenix, iFlagstaff, iLas Vegas neSalt Lake City.
U-Rosa kulindeleke ukuba abe e-Fenix ngoLwesibini, kuba kuza kubanda ngobusuku bomvulo.
I-National Weather Service yasePhoenix yathi nge-tweet: "Ukususela ngowe-1950 kukho iinyikima ezilishumi kuphela ezikhuselekileyo ezikhokelela kwi-tropical storm okanye kwi-depression kummandla oziikhilomitha ezingama-200 ukusuka ePhoenix!"
UKatrina (1967) yayisisiphepho esikufutshane nemida yaseArizona, kwiikhilomitha eziyi-40.
Iimodeli zakutshanje zeNational Hurricane Center zithi kuza neentsimbi ezi-5 ukuya kwezi-10 zemvula, ibe xa zithe qwa zingaba ziisentimitha eziyi-15 eMogollon Rim, eArizona.
Ezinye iindawo ezisemzantsi-ntshona weentlango, kuquka iintaba zaseRocky ezikwingqi eliphakathi neGreat Basin, ziza kufumana imvula engamasentimitha amathathu ukuya kwamashumi amahlanu, yaye apha naphaya kusenokubakho iisentimitha ezilishumi.
Kwiindawo ezingenazo izikhukula, imvula yaseRosa inokuba yintsikelelo kuba le ndawo ichaphazeleka yimbalela.
Nangona izikhukula zixhalabisa kakhulu, kusenokwenzeka ukuba ezinye zezo mvula ziya kuba luncedo kuba umzantsi-ntshona ngoku unamaxesha omkhenkce.
Ngokutsho kwe-U.S. Drought Monitor, imephu ebonisa iindawo ezomileyo ngoku, ngaphezu nje kwe-40 pesenti yeArizona inembalela encinane yembalela, eyesibini kwelona candelo liphezulu,  ingxelo ye-weather.com.
Inkanyamba uRosa ifikelela kwilizwekazi laseMexico, kwiNhlonhlo yeBaja California.
URosa usasebenza ngamandla xa kukho inkanyamba ngeCawa ekuseni, ibe umoya uphefumla ngesantya esiphezulu se-140 km ngeyure, uye umgama weekhilomitha eziyi-620 kumzantsi wePunta Eugenia, eMexico, uze uqhubele emantla ngesantya esiziikhilomitha eziyi-20 ngeyure.
Esi saqhwithi sibetha amanzi abandayo kwiLwandlekazi iPacific, nto leyo eyasiphelisa amandla aso.
Ngoko ke, kulindeleke ukuba ifike eMexico ngoMvulo emva kwemini okanye ngokuhlwa ngamandla eshushu.
Kunokuba nemvula eninzi kwiindawo ezithile eMexico, nto leyo ebangela ukuba kubekho izikhukula.
Iimvula eziphakathi kwe-8 ne-15 cm zilungele ukuwa ukusuka eBaa California ukuya kumantla ntshona eSonora, zifikelela kwi-25 cm, weather.com yaxela.
URosa uhamba enyakatho eMexico njengesaqhwithi esishushu ngaphambi kokuba afike kumda weArizona ngoLwesibini ekuseni njengesiquphe sezulu, aze aqhube ngeLwesibini kusihlwa adlule eArizona aze aye kumazantsi eUtah.
"Eyona ngozi inkulu kulindeleke ukuba iRosa okanye umsila wayo ube kuyo imvula eninzi eBaja California, kumantla ntshona eSonora, nakumazantsi ntshona entlango", itsho njalo iNational Hurricane Center.
Le mvula kulindeleke ukuba ibangele izikhukula ezibulalayo, imingxuma entlango, neendawo ezentabeni.
