Amakhulu abulawa yinyikima, itsunami, kunye neendleko zonyango
NgoMgqibelo, abasemagunyeni bathi, inyikima enkulu neetsunami ezenzeka kwisiqithi saseIndonesia iSulawesi zabulala abantu abangama-384 yaye abaninzi kubo balahlwa ngumhlaba xa amaza amakhulu ehla elunxwemeni.
Ngolwesihlanu, amakhulu abantu ayehlanganisene kwibhotile elunxwemeni kwisixeko sasePalu, xa amaza ayehla asuka kumitha emithandathu ukuphakama, njengoko kwakusithiwa sekubonakala ngathi kusemini, abantu abaninzi bawela phantsi baza batshabalalisa yonke into eyayisendleleni.
Le tsunami yabangelwa yinyikima enamandla angama-7.5 kwisikalo seRichter.
"Xa kwabakho isoyikiso se-tsunami izolo, kwakukho abantu elunxwemeni, abazange baphephe ngoko nangoko, baza baba ngamaxhoba ayo", utshilo uSutopo Purwo Nugroho, isithethi se-Indonesia Bureau for Natural Disaster Relief BNPB, kwiingxelo ze-Jakarta.
UNugroho wathi: "Itsunami yabangela nezinye iingozi: yatsala iimoto, imithi, izindlu, yatshayisa yonke into esemhlabeni", wongezelela esithi le tsunami yayihamba ngesantya esiziikhilomitha ezingama-800 ngeyure elwandle ngaphambi kokuba ifike kunxweme.
Wathi abanye abantu bakhwela emthini ukuze baphephe itsunami baze basinde.
Abantu abamalunga ne-16,700 bagudulwa baza bathunyelwa kwiindawo ezingama-24 zasePalu.
Imifanekiso evela emoyeni ekhutshwe yi-Natural Disaster Relief Agency ibonisa ukuba izakhiwo ezininzi neeveki zonakele, iibhulorho zaguquke zaza zabhidlika, yaye iMosque ingqongwe ngamanzi.
NgoMgqibelo, isixeko esiselunxwemeni saqhubeka sinyikima ngenxa yokungcangcazela.
Ezi zantlitha zantlitha zavakala kwindawo ekwakhiwe kuyo abantu abazizigidi ezingama-2.4.
I-Indonesia's Agency for the Assessment and Application of Technology (i-BPPT) yathi kwintshumayelo yayo, amandla akhutshwa yinyikima enkulu eyayenzeke ngoLwesihlanu ayimalunga nama-200 amandla ebekhoyo xa kuthelekiswa nebhombu le-athomu elawela iHiroshima kwiMfazwe Yehlabathi II.
Wathi kusenokwenzeka ukuba indawo yesixeko, esikude kwelo cala lide, yayibangele ukuba i-tsunami ibe nkulu.
UNugroho wathi umonakalo ubonakala kakhulu, esithi amawaka amakhaya, izibhedlele, iindawo zokuthenga neehotele zabhidlika.
Wathi abanye abantu ababulalayo babesele behleli phantsi kwezindlu eziwileyo, abantu abamalunga ne-540 belimala yaye abangama-29 belahlekile.
UNugroho wathi inani labantu ababuleweyo kunye nomonakalo unokuba mkhulu kunalo lonke unxweme olukho kwiikhilomitha ezingama-300 kumantla ePalu, kwindawo ebizwa ngokuba yiDonggala, ekufutshane nendawo yokuzamazama komhlaba.
UNugroho uthi, "Ukunxibelelana noDonggala kusilele ngokupheleleyo, asinalo naluphi na ulwazi".
Abantu abangaphezu kwe-300 000 bahlala apho, "kwathetha uMbutho weMfazwe oMhlophe.
"Oku sele kuyintshutshiso, kodwa kusenokuba kubi nangakumbi", kutsho uMnqamlezo Olubomvu.
NgoMgqibelo, le nkampani yagxekwa kakhulu ngenxa yokungachazi ukuba iPalu iye yafikelwa sisithokothoko, nangona abasebenzi bathi amaza afikelele kweli lizwe ngexesha lokulumkisa.
