Nanini na ndithetha phambi koluntu, nokuba ndithini, kukho amaqela ahlabayo kumajelo asekuhlaleni abhengeza ukuba ndiphikiswe ukuba ndibe lilungu lePalamente kunyulo oluzayo, atyhila imigaqo-nkqubo yeCentral andixelelwa ukuba ndingafanele ndibe lilungu leLabour.
