Ukuba icandelo lemfundo linokuyila lize liphumeze iikharityhulam zesikolo ezenziwe ngokwezifiso, siyabona ukuba iilwimi zanamhlanje zisaqhubeka ziyimfundo ethandwayo nezifunwa kakhulu ezikolweni.
