UMongameli uDonald Trump uqala ngolu suku eWheeling, eNtshona Virginia, uthotho olude lweentlanganiso zokhetho
Le yimiboniso yokuqala emihlanu kaTrump ekucwangciswe ukuba izakwenziwa kwiveki ezayo, kuquka imingcelele kwiindawo azithandayo, kuquka iTennessee neMississippi.
Ngoku ekubeni ukuvotelwa komntu amnyula ukuba abe ngumviwa weNkundla Ephakamileyo kuvaliwe, uTrump ufuna ukwakha inkxaso kunyulo oluzayo, kuba amaRiphablikhi asengozini yokulahlekelwa lulawulo lweCongress xa kuvotelwa ngoNovemba.
Uqala nini umngcelele kaTrump eWest Virginia ngokuhlwa, yaye ubukele njani kwi-intanethi?
Umsitho kaTrump eWheeling, eNtshona Virginia, uqala namhlanje, ngoMgqibelo, Septemba 29, 2018, ngo-19:00.
Unokuyibukela itrayi kaTrump eNtshona Virginia kwi-intanethi kwi-YouTube.
UTrump usenokuba uthetha ngeentlanganiso zomntu ozakufuna ukuba nguMgwebi Omkhulu uBrett Kavanaugh kule veki, eziye zahlawulwa ngakumbi ngokuzityholwa kukaKavanaugh ngokuziphatha kakubi ngokwesondo kwaye mhlawumbi iSenate iza kulinda iveki ukuba ivume ukuqeshwa kwakhe ngelixa iFBI iphengulula eli tyala.
Kodwa eyona njongo iphambili yale mibuthano kukuxhasa abo baviwa yiRiphabliki kunyulo lukaNovemba ukuze bafumane amandla.
Iqela elikhokela uMongameli Trump lithi ezi ntlanganiso zintlanu eziza kubakho kwiveki ezayo zenzelwe ukukhuthaza amavolontiya kunye nabalandeli, ngelixa amaRiphablikhi ezama ukukhusela nokwandisa uninzi lwawo kwiSenate nakwiNdlu yeeNdlu, ngokutsho kweReuters.
"Ulawulo lweCongress lubaluleke kakhulu kwinkqubo yakhe, kangangokuba umongameli uye kumazwe amaninzi kangangoko kunokwenzeka njengoko ixesha lokunyusa liphuma", utshilo isithethi somkhankaso kaTrump, esafuna ukungachazwanga ngegama.
Umsitho we-Wesbanco Arena eWheeling namhlanje unokutsala abalandeli abavela eOhio nasePennsylvania baze baxutyushwe kumajelo eendaba asePittsburgh, utshilo iWest Virginia Metro News.
NgoMgqibelo, uTrump uye watyelela iWest Virginia okwesibini kule nyanga idlulileyo, ilizwe awathi waliphumelelayo ngo-2016 ngamaphesenti angaphezu kwama-40.
UTrump uzama ukunceda umviwa weSizwe waseNtshona Virginia, uPatrick Morrisey, ohlala emva kwevoti.
"Asikho isibonakaliso esihle sokuba uMorrisey kufuneka eze kumongameli ukuze amnike amandla okwenza unyulo", utshilo uSimon Haeder, isazi ngezepolitiki kwiYunivesithi yaseWest Virginia, ngokweReuters.
Iqela lase-USA lizimisele ukulwa ukuze ithemba lihlale liphila ngaphambi kwee-singles zika-Sonto
Emva kweentlanganiso ezintathu zenkqubo enye, i-Foursomes yangoMgqibelo emva kwemini isenokuba yayiyiloo nto yayifuneka kule nkomfa yeRyder Cup.
Umqhubi wezihlandlo othengekayo ngumdlalo owenziwe ngokugqibeleleyo, kodwa okwenene abadlali bayakholelwa kuwo, ingakumbi kwiingqungquthela ezinje.
Ngoko ke, ngubani okwangoku onamathuba aphezulu?
