IYurophu ilawula nge-10-6 ngosuku lokugqibela lweRyder Cup
IYurophu iqala ngomkhamo omhle kakhulu ngomhla wokugqibela weRyder Cup, emva kweebhola ezine neebhola ezine ngoMgqibelo, iqhekeza liqhube iUnited States nge-10-6.
UTommy Fleetwood noFrancesco Molinari, ababini ababekhuthazekile, bahola iqela labo ngokuphumelela kabini ngaphezu kukaTiger Woods, owayenengxaki, nto leyo eyabenza baphumelela ngeephuzu ezine kwiLe Golf National.
Iqela laseYurophu likaThomas Bjorn, elifuna ukubuyisa indebe elayilahleka eHazeltine kwiminyaka emibini edluleyo, lalinamandla kunalawo aseMerika awayengayiqondi kakuhle imidlalo ye-Fourball yasekuseni, nge-3-1.
I-US yanikela umva kwi-foursomes, apho yaphumelela khona imidlalo emibini, kodwa ayizange ikwazi ukuwufumana umva wayo.
Iqela likaJim Furyk kufuneka lifumane amanqaku asibhozo kwimidlalo eli-12 yeqonga likaLwesine ukuze liqhubeke lifumana le ndebe.
UFleetwood ngowokuqala ovela eYurophu ukuba aphumelele ngamanqaku amane ngokulandelelana, ngoxa yena noMolinari, owaziwa ngokuba nguMolliwood, emva kweveki ehlaziyiweyo, baba ngowesibini kwimbali yeRyder Cup ukuba baphumelele ngamanqaku amane kwimidlalo yabo emine yokuvula.
Emva kokubetha uWoods noPatrick Reed kwi-four-ball, babedlala kakuhle, bebetha uWoods odimazekileyo kunye nomntu omtsha waseMerika uBryyson Dechambeau nge-5 ne-4.
UWoods, owathi emva kwemidlalo emibini ngoMgqibelo wazama ukubonisa umdla omhle, kodwa ngoku uphulukene nemidlalo eyi-19 kweye-29 kwi-four-balls, kwi-four-somes, yaye une-7 elandelanayo.
UJustin Rose, oqeqeshwe kakuhle kwiimbumbulu ezine zentsasa ka-, wabuyela kwiqabane lakhe uHenrik Stenson kwiimbumbulu ezine, yaye bebonke boyisa uDustin Johnson noBrooks Koepka, ababengamanani amabini anesithathu ehlabathini, nge-2&1.
Kodwa ke, kwakungekho nto iphosakeleyo ngeYurophu ngale mini imnandi, apho kwakukho umoya omnyama kumzantsi-ntshona weParis.
UJordan Spieth, owakha waphumelela izihlandlo ezithathu kwiMajor, noJustin Thomas babeka umlinganiselo wamaMerika ngamaphuzu amathathu ngoMgqibelo.
Emva komdlalo onzima, baphumelela nge-2&1 kwiibhola ezine zeSpanish uJon Rahm noIan Poulter, baza kamva boyisa uPoulter noRory McIlroy nge-4&3 kwii-foursomes, emva kokuphulukana nemingxunya emine yokuqala.
Kwizihlandlo ezibini kuphela kwimbali yeRyder Cup iqela liye lakwazi ukufikelela kwi-4-point lag ekuqaleni kwee-singles, nangona iqela likaFuryk linamathuba amaninzi okudibanisa, njengoko ngoku lifumana indebe.
Kodwa ngoku sele kudlule iintsuku ezimbini behlala kwindawo yesibini, kubonakala ngathi ukuhlaselwa ngeCawa kwakugqithiseleyo.
I-North Korea ithi ayizukuze i-unilaterally disarm without trust
UMphathiswa Wezangaphandle waseMntla Korea waxelela iZizwe Ezimanyeneyo ngoMgqibelo ukuba izibheno eziqhubekayo zikhokelela ekwandeni kokungathembani eUnited States yaye phantsi kweemeko ezinjalo, ilizwe aliyi kukwazi ukuyeka ngokungenammiselo izixhobo zalo zenyukliya.
URi Yong Ho uxelele iNdibano yeZizwe eziManyeneyo yonyaka ukuba uMntla Korea uye wenza "amanyathelo abalulekileyo okuthembeka" kulo nyaka uphelileyo, njengokuyeka ukuvavanya izixhobo zenyukliya neendlwana, ukuchitha indawo yokuvavanya izixhobo zenyukliya, nokuzibophelela ekungasasazeni izixhobo zenyukliya nobuchwepheshe.
Noko ke, asinakubona mpendulo efanayo evela eU.S.
Ngaphandle kokuthembela ngokupheleleyo eUnited States, akukho themba lokhuseleko lwethu lwesizwe, yaye phantsi kweemeko ezinjalo asiyi kuzenzela nto ngokungekho ngqiqweni.
Nangona uRi ephindaphinda izikhalo ezaziwayo zaseNyakatho Korea zokumelana neWashington ngendlela 'yokuxhathisa' ukuqhushumba kweenqwelo-moya, apho iNyakatho Korea yayiza kuvuzwa njengoko isenza amanyathelo, waphawula ukuba akazange akwalile unilateral denuclearisation, njengoko kwakusenziwa yiPyongyang ngaphambili.
URi wabhekisela kwingxelo ehlangeneyo kaKim Jong Un noDonald Trump ngexesha lokuqala kakhulu kwintlanganiso phakathi komongameli wase-US osebenzayo kunye nenkokeli yase-North Korea ngoJuni 12 eSingapore, xa uKim wathembisa ukusebenza kwi-denuclearisation ye-Korea Peninsula ngelixa uTrump wathembisa iziqinisekiso zokhuseleko lwase-North Korea.
I-North Korea ifuna ukuphelisa ngokusemthethweni imfazwe yaseKorea ka-1950-53, kodwa iUnited States ithi iPyongyang imele iqale ilahle izixhobo zayo zenyukliya.
IWashington iphinde yachasana nemibongo yokunciphisa izigwebo ezinzima zamazwe ngamazwe ezibekwe uMntla Korea.
US uyafuna ukukhanyela i-nuclear first kwaye unyusa uxinzelelo ngokusebenzisa izohlwayo ukuze zifezekise injongo yazo ngendlela enyanzelisayo, kwaye nokuba zichasene nokuvakaliswa kokuphela kwemfazwe, utshilo uRi.
Ingcamango yokuba isohlwayo sinokusenza siguquke isisiqhushumbisi sabantu abangenalo ulwazi ngathi.
Kodwa ingxaki kukuba, ezi zityholo ziqhubekayo zenza singathembani.
URi akazange athethe ngecebo lokudibana okwesibini kukaKim noTrump, into eyacetyiswa yinkokeli yaseMerika kwiZizwe eziManyeneyo ekuqaleni kweveki.
Kunoko, lo mphathiswa wagxininisa kwiintlanganiso ezintathu ezenziwa nguKim kunye nenkokeli yaseMzantsi Korea uMune Jae-in kwiinyanga ezintlanu ezidlulileyo, waza wongezelela wathi: "Ukuba elinye icala kulo mbandela wokurhoxisa kwakunguMzantsi Korea, kungekhona iUnited States, urhoxiso lweKorea lwalungeke lufike kuloo ndawo.
Nangona kunjalo, ithoni yentetho kaRi yahluke kakhulu kunonyaka ophelileyo, xa wathi kwiNdibano yeZizwe eziManyeneyo ukuba akunakuphepheka ukuba iirobhothi zaseMntla Korea zibhekise kumhlaba waseMerika emva kokuba uMongameli uTrump uKim ethe indoda yeerobhothi iya kuzibulala.
UTrump, owayesongela ukuyitshabalalisa ngokupheleleyo iNyakatho Korea kunyaka ophelileyo, wadumisa uKim kulo nyaka kwiZizwe eziManyeneyo ngesibindi sakhe sokuthatha amanyathelo okucima izixhobo, kodwa wathi kusekuninzi okumele kwenziwe kwaye kufuneka kuqhubeke nezifungo de iNyakatho Korea ingabi namathumba.
NgoLwesithathu, uTrump wathi akanalo ixesha lokuyenza le nto: "Nokuba ithatha iminyaka emibini, emithathu okanye iinyanga ezintlanu, akunandaba".
I-China ne-Russia zithi i-UN Security Council kufuneka ihlawulise iPyongyang ngenxa yamanyathelo athathwe.
Noko ke, ngoLwesine, uNobhala Wezangaphandle waseMerika uMike Pompeo wathi kwiBhunga Lezokhuseleko leZizwe Ezimanyeneyo: "Ukugcinwa kwezo zityholo zeBhunga Lezokhuseleko kufuneka kuqhubeke ngamandla nangokuqinileyo de sifezekise ukucinywa kwenyukliya ngokupheleleyo, okugqibeleleyo nokuqinisekisiweyo".
Ukususela ngo-2006, iBhunga leZokhuseleko liye laphumeza izigwebo ngokuvumelanayo nxamnye neNyakatho Korea ukuze linciphise kakhulu imali yeprogram yasePyongyang yeenyukliya neebhalikhi.
UPompeo wadibana noRi ngaphandle kweNdibano Jikelele yeZizwe eziManyeneyo, wathi uza kubuyela ePyongyang kwinyanga ezayo ukuze alungiselele intlanganiso yesibini.
UPompeo uye watyelela eMntla Korea kathathu kulo nyaka, kodwa utyelelo lwakhe lokugqibela aluzange lube luhle.
Kwiiyure nje ezimbalwa emva kokuba emkile ePyongyang ngoJulayi, esithi kukho inkqubela phambili, iNyakatho Korea yamtyhola ngokubeka 'imfuno eziphosakeleyo.'
Kulo nyanga, uMzantsi Korea uthembise ukuchitha indawo yokuthutha izikhali kunye nenkundla yenyukliya ukuba iUnited States ithatha amanyathelo afanelekileyo.
Uthi uKim wamxelela ukuba amanyathelo afanelekileyo afuna ukuwathatha, ziinkqubo zokhuseleko ezazithenjisiwe nguTrump eSingapore, kunye neenyathelo eziya kuqhubeka nokuqhelaniswa nobudlelwane baseWashington.
Abafundi baseHarvard bafunda ngokubaluleka kokuphumla ngokwaneleyo
Iklasi entsha yaseHarvard kulo nyaka yenza ukuba bonke abafundi balale ngokwaneleyo, ukuze balwe nenkcubeko ekhulayo yama-macho ekhangeleka ipholile ukuchitha ubusuku bonke befunda, besela i-caffeine eninzi.
Omnye uprofesa wafumanisa ukuba abafundi beyona yunivesithi inkulu ehlabathini badla ngokungazi ukuba yintoni eyona nto ibalulekileyo ukuze bakwazi ukuzixhasa.
UCharles Czeisler, onguprofesa wezokwelapha zokulala kwiHarvard Medical School, kunye nengcali enxulumene neBrigham and Women's Hospital, wenza le khosi, njengoko esazi, iyingqayizivele eUnited States.
Wacinga ukuqala ikhosi emva kokuba ethethe ngendlela ukungalali kakuhle okunokuchaphazela ngayo ukufunda.
"Ekupheleni kwentetho yam, kweza intombazana kum yaza yathi, 'Kutheni ndingakuva oku nje, kunyaka wam wokugqibela?'
Wathi akukho mntu wakha wamxelela ukuba ukulala kubalulekile, nto leyo eyandothusayo", watsho watsho kwiThe Telegraph.
Kwisifundo esiza kuqhutywa okokuqala kulo nyaka, abafundi baya kufundiswa imigaqo-siseko yendlela indlela yokulala kakuhle enokubanceda ngayo baphucule imfundo yabo kunye nemidlalo yabo, baze baphucule impilo yabo ngokubanzi.
UPaul Barreira, onguprofesa wezifo zengqondo kwiHarvard Medical School nomphathi wezeMpilo kwiYunivesithi, wathi le yunivesithi yagqiba ekubeni ibambe le klasi xa kwafunyaniswa ukuba abafundi babengenalo ixesha lokulala kakhulu ebudeni beveki.
Le khosi ithatha iyure enye yaye iquka uthotho lwemisebenzi enxibelelanayo.
Kwinxalenye enye, abafundi babona umfanekiso wegumbi lokulala, apho becofa kwiikopi zekofu, iirente, izixhobo zokuzilolonga neencwadi ukuze bafunde ngakumbi ngemiphumo yecaffeine nokukhanya nendlela ukusebenza kwezemidlalo okuchaphazeleka ngayo kukungalali, nokubaluleka kokulala rhoqo.
Kwelinye icandelo, abantu ababelapho bafunda ngendlela ukungalali ngokwaneleyo okwandisa ngayo umngcipheko wokuhlaselwa yintliziyo, ukuhlaselwa sisifo somzimba, ukudandatheka nomhlaza.
Ukusebenzisa umfanekiso wekhampasi, onemifanekiso esondeleleneyo, kukhuthazwa abafundi ukuba bacinge ngemihla ngemihla.
Siyazi ukuba asiyi kuyitshintsha ngoko nangoko indlela yokuziphatha kwabafundi.
Kodwa sivakalelwa kukuba banelungelo lokwazi konke oku, kanye njengokuba abantu benelungelo lokwazi ukuba ukhetho lwabo lwecuba lunempembelelo njani kwimpilo yabo, wongezelela uCheisler.
Uthi, inkcubeko yokuzingca ngokufunda ubusuku bonke isekho, yaye ngenxa yetekhnoloji yanamhlanje noxinzelelo olukhulayo kubafundi, ukungalali kakuhle kuyingxaki enkulu.
Wathi ukulala ngokwaneleyo, umgangatho ophezulu, umele ube sisixhobo esifihlakeleyo somfundi sokulwa noxinzelelo, ukukhathala, uloyiko, kwanokungafumani ubunzima, kuba ukungalali ngokwaneleyo kwenza ingqondo ibe nomdla ongapheliyo.
URaymond So, oneminyaka eli-19 ubudala waseCalifornia, ofunda ngeekhemikhali neebhayoloji, wanceda uProfesa Czeisler ekuqulunqeni esi sifundo, kuba wayesele efundiswe nguProfesa xa wayesemnyakeni wakhe wokuqala eHarvard kunyaka ophelileyo.
Wathi esi sikolo samvulela amehlo, samkhuthaza ukuba afunde ukuze afumane izifundo zakhe kubo bonke abantu abakwikhampasi.
Ithemba lakhe kukuba, eli nyathelo lilandelayo kukucela bonke abafundi ukuba bafunde ngendlela efanayo ngaphambi kokuba baye kwisikolo esikhuphisanayo.
UProfesa Czeisler ucebisa abafundi ukuba babeke i-alamu ngaphambi kokuba balale, kungekhona nje i-alamu yokuvuka, kodwa nokuba baqaphele imiphumo emibi yokukhanya okuhlaza okuvela kwizikrini ze-elektroniki nakwizibane ze-elektroniki, ezinokuphazamisa umjikelo wakho wokulala, nto leyo enokwenza kube nzima ukulala.
I-Livingston 1 - 0 Rangers: Injongo kaMenga yenza amadoda kaGerrard ahambe phantsi
I-Ranger yaphinda yafumana umdlalo wayo udimazayo xa uDolly Menga waphumelela, kwaye iqela elibuthathaka likaSteven Gerrard lahlulwa ngo-1-0 e-Livingston.
Iqela laseIbrox lalinethemba lokufumana impumelelo yokuqala kumdlalo wokugqibela ukususela ngoFebruwari xa lathimba iSt Johnstone ngo-4-1, kodwa iqela likaGary Holt labangela ukulahleka, phantse okwesibini kuGerrard njengomlawuli kwimidlalo eli-18.
