NgoMgqibelo, iNew York iza kuba neGlobal Citizen Festival, umsitho womculo waminyaka le oza kuboniswa ngabantu abaninzi abanomdla, abaza kuba nomsebenzi ofanayo: ukuphelisa ubuhlwempu ehlabathini.
Okwesixhenxe, amashumi amawaka abantu aya kuza kwiGreat Lawn eCentral Park ukuze abukele iGlobal Citizen Festival, kungekuphela nje ukuze bonwabele izinto ezifana noJanet Jackson, uCardi B noShawn Mendes kodwa ukuze bavuselele ulwazi malunga nenjongo yokwenene: ukuphelisa ubuhlwempu ngokugqithiseleyo ngo-2030.
I-Global Citizen Festival, eyaqala ngo-2012, yandisa i-Global Poverty Project, iqela labaxhasi behlabathi jikelele abanethemba lokuqeda ubuhlwempu ngokunyusa inani labantu abazama ukulwa nalo.
Abaphulaphuli abafuna ukufumana itikiti le-VIP simahla (ngaphandle kokuba babezimisele ukuhlawula itikiti le-VIP), kwakufuneka benze imisebenzi emininzi, okanye 'iinkqubo' ezinjengokuvolontiya, ukuthumela i-imeyile kumlawuli wehlabathi, ukwenza umnxeba okanye ukwenza enye indlela ebalulekileyo yokuzisa ulwazi ngenjongo: ukuphelisa ubuhlwempu.
