Ummeli waseMerika utyhola iChina 'ngokuxhaphaza' ngeentengiso 'zentshabalalo'
Kwiveki emva kokuba iphephandaba laseTshayina elisemthethweni labeka intengiso yamaphepha amane ephephandabeni laseMerika, eyayincoma iinzuzo zokurhweba phakathi kweUnited States neTshayina, ummeli waseMerika eChina watyhola iBeijing ngokusebenzisa amajelo eendaba aseMerika ukuze asasaze intetho.
UMongameli waseMerika uDonald Trump kutshanje ubhekisele kwi-China Daily's paid attachment kwiDes Moines Register, iphephandaba elithengisa kakhulu eIowa, emva kokuthetha ngeChina yokungenelela kunyulo lweCongress lukaNovemba 6, ityala eliphikwa yiChina.
Ngokutsho kwabasemagunyeni baseMerika abacatshulwe yiReuters, isityholo sikaTrump sokuba iBeijing izama ukungenelela kunyulo lwaseMerika, sibonisa ukuba eli phulo litsha liza kuba yintshukumo enkulu kwiphulo likaWashington lokucinezela iChina.
Nangona kuyinto eqhelekileyo ukuba oorhulumente bamanye amazwe babeke iintengiso zokukhuthaza urhwebo, iBeijing neWashington ngoku zikwimfazwe yorhwebo ekhulayo, apho ziye zahlawulisana amaxabiso aphakamileyo okuthumela izinto kwamanye amazwe.
Amaxabiso okuphindezela eTshayina ekuqaleni kwemfazwe yorhwebo ayejoliswe ngokukodwa ekufumaneni abathengisi kumazwe afana neIowa, abaxhasa iRiphabhlikhi kaTrump, njengoko iingcali zaseTshayina nezaseMerika zithe.
UTerry Branstad, ummeli waseMerika eChina, nowayesakuba nguRhuluneli waseIowa, owayengumthengisi omkhulu weemveliso zolimo eChina, wathi iChina iye yahlasela abasebenzi baseMerika, amafama kunye namashishini.
"I-China", njengoko uBranstad wabhala kwiphepha-ndaba laseDes Moines Register ngeCawa, "ngoku iphindaphindwe kabini le mbambano ngokushicilela iintengiso zentshutshiso kwiphephandaba lethu elikhululekileyo".
UBranstad wabhala wathi: "Ngokusasaza le ngxelo, urhulumente waseTshayina usebenzisa inkululeko yokuthetha neyeza, isithethe esithe sahlala ixesha elide eMelika ngokuthumela intengiso ehlawulwayo kwiDes Moines Register".
Wabhala wathi: "Ngokwahlukileyo koko, kwi-kiosk ese-centre of Beijing, uya kufumana amazwi ahlukeneyo, yaye awuyi kubona ukuhlukahluka kweembono zabantu baseTshayina ngendlela ekunzima ngayo ukuqhubeka koqoqosho, kuba amajelo eendaba elawulwa ngamandla yiCawa YamaTshayina".
Wongezelela esithi "enye yezona ziphephandaba ziphambili eChina iye yala ukupapasha inqaku layo", ngokungathi ayitsho ukuba yeyiphi iphephandaba eli.
