"Asikokhetho nje kuphela olwenziwa yikomiti, okanye olwenziwa ekugqibeleni okanye uKavanaugh efakwa enkundleni, kodwa yindlela amaRiphablikhi amele ukuba amgcine ngayo", utshilo uGuy Cecil, umlawuli wePriorities USA, iqela elinceda amaDemocrat ukuba akhethwe, ecacisa kwijelo leendaba.
Noko ke, amaMerika abonakala engavumelaniyo ukuba ngubani amthembayo emva kobungqina bukaFord noKavanaugh, apho ininzi elincinane lisayine icala lalowo wokugqibela.
Uhlolisiso olutsha olwenziwe nguYouGov lubonisa ukuba iipesenti ezingama-41 zabaphenduli bayakholelwa ngokuqinisekileyo okanye mhlawumbi ubungqina bukaFord yaye iipesenti ezingama-35 bayakholelwa ngokuqinisekileyo okanye mhlawumbi uKavanaugh.
Ngaphezu koko, ama-38% athi acinga ukuba uKavanaugh wayexoka ngokuqinisekileyo okanye mhlawumbi xa wayefakaza, ngoxa ama-30% kuphela awayesithi uFord wayexoka.
Emva kokukhuthazwa nguFlake, i-FBI ngoku iphinda iphonononge izityholo zikaFord nezomnye umtshutshisi, uDeborah Ramirez, njengoko ingxelo yeThe Guardian.
