Umvelisi weWebhu yeHlabathi lonke uceba i-Intanethi entsha ukuze ajongane neGoogle neFacebook
UTim Berners-Lee, owasungula iWebhu yeHlabathi, uqala ukuqalisa ishishini elifuna ukhuphisana neFacebook, iAmazon neGoogle.
I-Inrupt, eyona projekthi intsha ye-tech legend, yinkampani esekwe kwiqonga elivulekileyo lomthombo ozimeleyo u-Berners-Lee.
I-Solid inika abasebenzisi ithuba lokukhetha ukuba bafumane phi na ulwazi lwabo kwaye ngubani ofumana ulwazi.
Kwi-Introduction, uBerners-Lee wathi "ukulawula kwehlabathi" yeyona nto iphambili kwi-Inrupt.
Wathi xa ethetha ngokuqalisa.
"Eli lixesha lembali".
Le app isebenzisa iteknoloji kaSolide ukuze abantu bakwazi ukwenza 'ugcino lwedatha lomntu siqu kwi-intanethi' okanye i-POD.
Unokulondoloza uluhlu lwabantu onxibelelana nabo, uluhlu lwemisebenzi, ikhalenda, ithala leengoma nezinye izixhobo zobuqu nezobuchule.
Kunjengokuba iGoogle Drive, iMicrosoft Outlook, iSlack neSpotify zonke zifumaneka kunye kwibrowser enye kwaye zonke ngexesha elinye.
Into eyenza i-POD ibe yinto ekhethekileyo kukuba ixhomekeke ngokupheleleyo kumsebenzisi ukuba ngubani ofumana loluphi ulwazi.
Le nkampani ibiza oku ngokuthi 'ukuxhaswa kwedatha ukuze umntu abe namandla.'
Ngokutsho kukaJohn Bruce, uMlawuli weNkampani, ingcamango ye-Inrupt kukuba le nkampani inika izixhobo, iinkqubo nezakhono ezifunekayo ukuze iSolid ifumaneke kubo bonke.
Le nkampani ngoku iquka uBerners-Lee, uBruce, iqonga lokhuseleko elithengwe yi-IBM, abaphuhlisi abathile abaqeshwe ukuba basebenze kule projekthi, kunye noluntu lwabaprogram abazinikeleyo.
Ukususela kule veki, abaphuhlisi bezobuchwepheshe ehlabathini lonke banokuzenzela iiapps zabo ezikhuselekileyo besebenzisa izixhobo ezikhoyo kwiwebhusayithi ye-Inrupt.
UBerners-Lee wathi yena neqela lakhe abayi kuthetha "noFacebook noGoogle malunga nokwenza okanye ukungawenzi utshintsho olupheleleyo oluya kuthi lubeke zonke iimodeli zabo zeshishini ezingqondweni zabo ngaxeshanye".
"Asinakucela imvume yabo".
Kwiposti kwiMedium epapashwe ngoMgqibelo, uBerners-Lee wabhala ukuba "umsebenzi (ka-Inrupt) kukubonelela ngombane wezorhwebo kunye ne-ecosystem enceda ukukhusela ukuzinza kunye nomgangatho wewebhu entsha eyakhiwe kwiSolid".
Ngowe-1994 uBerners-Lee waguqula i-intanethi xa waseka iWorld Wide Web Consortium kwi-Massachusetts Institute of Technology.
Kwiinyanga ezidlulileyo uBerners-Lee uye waba lizwi elinamandla kwingxoxo yokungathathi cala kwenethiwekhi.
Emva kokumiselwa kwe-Inrupt, uBerners-Lee uya kuqhubeka engumqalisi kunye nomlawuli weWorld Wide Web Consortium, iWeb Foundation kunye ne-Open Data Institute.
UBerners-Lee wongezelela wathi: "Ndiqinisekile ukuba eli lixesha elitsha kwiWebhu".
UBernard Vann: Umfundisi nomphathi weVictoria Cross weMfazwe Yehlabathi I
Umfundisi weCawa yaseNgilani kuphela owanikwa iVictoria Cross ngexesha leMfazwe Yehlabathi I njengomkhosi wenkokeli yomkhosi uyahlonitshwa kwiminyaka eli-100 kamva kwidolophu awazalelwa kuyo.
U-Lt. Colonel, u-Bernard Vann, wafumana le mbeko ngenxa yokuhlaselwa kweBellenglise neLehaucourt ngoSeptemba 29, 1918.
Noko ke, wabulawa ngumdubuli kwiintsuku ezine kamva, ngoko akazange azi ukuba wanikwa imbeko ephakamileyo yemikhosi yaseBritani.
Ilitye lesikhumbuzo lavulwa ngoonyana bakhe ababini abazukulwana xa babethwele abantu eRushden, eNorthamptonshire, ngoMgqibelo.
Omnye wabazukulwana, uMichael Vann, wathi 'yayingumfuziselo oqaqambileyo' ukuba ilitye lachazwa kwiminyaka eli-100 emva kokuba utatomkhulu wakhe enikezele.
Ngokutsho kweLondon Gazette, ngoSeptemba 29, 1918, uLt. Col. Vann wakhokela iqela lakhe ngaphaya kweCanal de Saint-Quentin "kwiphunga elikhulu nangaphantsi komlilo omkhulu wemipu nezikhali".
Kamva, waqhushumbisa waya kumgca womlilo waza wakhokela umgca phambili ngaphambi kokuba agxume aye kumpu wasemagqagaleni aze abulale amalungu amathathu eqela.
ULt. Colonel Vann wabulawa ngumdubuli waseJamani ngo-Oktobha 4, 1918, kwinyanga nje engaphambi kokuphela kwemfazwe.
UMichael Vann, oneminyaka engama-72, wathi izenzo zikagogo wakhe "zazingayi kuba yinto endiyaziyo ukuba andinakukwazi ukuyiqonda kodwa zikwabangela ndizive ndithobekile".
Yena nomntakwabo uGqr. James Vann babeka omnye umnqwazi emva kwendibano eyayikhokelwa yiBrentwood Imperial Youth Band.
UMichael Vann wathi "waziva enentlonelo enkulu ngokudlala indima yakhe kulo msitho", yaye wongezelela wathi "inkuthazo yeqhawe lokwenene ibonakala kwinkxaso eliyifumana kubantu abaninzi".
