Inqanawa entsha yaseJamani yaphinda yahluthwa
I-Fregat entsha ye-Navy yaseJamani yayizakuqala ukusebenza ngo-2014, ithathe indawo yeenqanawa zemfazwe zexesha leMfazwe Yomlomo, kodwa kuya kuthatha unyaka omnye ngaphambi kokuba ilungele ukulungiswa ngenxa yeenkqubo ezonakeleyo kunye neendleko eziphezulu, kwaxelwa amajelo asekuhlaleni.
I-Rheinland-Pfalz, inqanawa ephambili kwi-Baden-Wuerttemberg-class frigates, ngoku ihambisiwe ukuya kwisiqingatha sokuqala sika-2019, ngokutsho kwephephandaba iDie Zeit, ecaphula isithethi somkhosi.
Le nqanawa ibiza kuba yinxalenye yoMkhosi wezasolwandle ngo-2014, kodwa iingxaki eziphazamisayo emva kokuziswa ziye zabangela ukuba le projekthi inqwenelekayo ingasebenzi.
Iinqanawa ezine zeBaden-Wuerttemberg eziyalelwe yiMarine ngo-2007 ziza kuthatha indawo yeefrigate zeBremen eziphelelwe lixesha.
Okoko sisazi, banesixhobo esinamandla, uthotho lweerhente zokulwa nomkhumbi, kunye nobuchwepheshe obuthile obungabonakaliyo, njengokunciphisa iiradar, i-infrared kunye neempawu ze-acoustic.
Ezinye izinto ezibalulekileyo ziimvavanyo zokugcina ixesha elide, kufuneka kube lula ukusebenzisa iinqanawa ezintsha kangangeminyaka emibini elandelelanayo, kude nezibuko lasekhaya.
Kodwa ke, ukulibaziseka okuqhubekayo kuthetha ukuba iinqanawa zemfazwe eziphambili ezijolise ekunikeni iJamani ithuba lokuqwalasela amandla azo aphesheya kweelwandle sele ziphelelwe lixesha xa ziqaliswa ukusebenza, utsho uDie Zeit.
I-F125 eyabulala abantu yayisabalala kakhulu kunyaka ophelileyo xa i-Navy yaseJamani yavuma ukuyisebenzisa yaza yabuyisela kwi-Blohm & Voss shipyard eHamburg.
Eli yayilixesha lokuqala ukuba iMarine ibuyisele inqanawa kumakhi wenqanawa emva kokuziswa kwayo.
Kunqabile ukwazi izizathu zokuba ibuyiselwe, kodwa amajelo eendaba aseJamani ayecaphula 'iziphene zesoftware nezesixhobo' eziya kwenza ukuba inqanawa ingasebenzi xa isetyenziswa kumsebenzi wokulwa.
Iziphene zesoftware zazibalulekile kuba iinqanawa zodidi lweBaden-Wuerttemberg zisetyenziswa ngabanini-mkhosi abangama-120 - isiqingatha samadoda kwiifrigate zodidi lwaseBremen.
Kwakhona kwacaca ukuba inqanawa inzima kakhulu, nto leyo eya kunciphisa ukusebenza kwayo ize inciphise amandla omkhosi wokwenza ulwandiso olongezelelekileyo.
I-Rheinland-Pfalz inobunzima obungama-7,000 eetoni, ephindwe kabini xa ithelekiswa neenqanawa ezikwiqela elifanayo nezo zaqhutywa ngamaJamani kwiMfazwe Yehlabathi II.
Ukongezelela kwizixhobo ezinesiphene, ixabiso leprojekthi epheleleyo, kuquka noqeqesho lwabasebenzi, liza kuba yingxaki.
Kuthiwa oku kuye kwafikelela kwi-â¬ 3.1 billion, xa kuthelekiswa ne-â¬ 2.2 billion yokuqala.
Iingxaki ezijongene neeflegi ezintsha zeenqanawa zibaluleke ngakumbi ngenxa yezilumkiso zakutshanje zokunciphisa amandla omkhosi wasemkhosini waseJamani.
Ekuqaleni kwalo nyaka, uHans-Peter Bartels, intloko yeKomiti Yokuzikhusela yaseJamani, wavuma ukuba enyanisweni, ulwandle "luye lwaswela iinqanawa ezinokusetyenziswa".
Igosa lathi le ngxaki iye yanda ngokuhamba kwexesha njengeqhwa, kuba iinqanawa ezindala ziye zapheliswa kodwa azange zifunyanwe.
Wakhalaza esithi kwakungekho phenyane lasemkhombeni leBaden-Wuerttemberg elaliza kufunyanwa ukuze liqulunqwe.
I-National Trust ifunda ubomi obungafihliyo beempuku
Uphando olutsha olwenziwe kwilali yaseScotland, luzama ukubonisa indlela iimbovane ezisebenzisa ngayo umhlaba ukuze zifumane ukutya.
Ithemba kukuba ezi zinto ziza kubangela ukuba kucace ngakumbi indlela ezihamba ngayo ezi zilwanyana zincinane, zize zikhuthaze ukwenziwa kwezinto eziza kulondolozwa kwixesha elizayo.
Olu phando lwenziwa ziingcali zeNational Trust for Scotland, lulandela i-brown dwarf mouse, i-brown big caterpillar mouse, ne-water caterpillar mouse kwi-Inverewe Gardens, eWester Ross.
Izixhobo zokurekhoda ezikhethekileyo zifakwe kwiindawo eziphambili ezijikeleze ipropathi ukuze zilandelwe imisebenzi yeempuku ngexesha lonyaka.
Abasebenzi be-NTS kunye namavolontiya baya kuqhuba iimvavanyo eziphathwayo besebenzisa iidetekhodi zesandla.
Uhlalutyo lwengoma oluchanileyo lwazo zonke izinto eziqokelelweyo luya kuqinisekisa ukuba i-batterfly iyagquma kangakanani yaye yenza ntoni.
Emva koko, kwenziwa imephu yendawo yokuhlala kunye nengxelo ukuze kuveliswe umfanekiso onenkcukacha ngendlela abaziphatha ngayo.
URob Dewar, umcebisi weNTS ngokukhusela indalo, unethemba lokuba iziphumo ziya kubonisa ukuba zeziphi iindawo zendawo yokuhlala ezibaluleke kakhulu kwiibhabhathane nendlela ezisetyenziswa ngayo.
Olu lwazi luya kunceda ekufumaneni izibonelelo zokulawula indawo yokuhlala, njengokudala amadlelo nendlela esinokuzigcina ngayo kakuhle amahlathi ukuze zihlale zifumaneka kwiibhabhathane nezinye iintlobo.
Iimveku zaseScotland nakwezinye iindawo zase-UK ziye zancipha kakhulu kule nkulungwane idlulileyo.
Zisengozini ngenxa yokwakha nokuphuhlisa izinto ezichaphazela indawo yokuhlala nokulahleka kweendawo ezihlala kuzo.
Iindawo ezinomoya kunye nemitha-mlilo nazo zinokuba yingozi, kanye njengeengcambu zokubhabha kunye nokulungiswa kwezinto zokwakha ngemichiza kunye nokuhlaselwa ziikati zasekhaya.
Iimpuku aziboni.
Noko ke, ngenxa yemikhwa yabo yokuzingela yasebusuku, iindlebe zabo ziluncedo ngakumbi kunamehlo abo xa kuthethwa ngokubambisa amaxhoba.
Basebenzisa ubuchule obuphambili bokujonga indawo ye-echo ukuze babone indawo yezinambuzane nezithuba ezikuyo.
I-NTS, elawula izakhiwo ezingaphezu kwe-270 zembali, iigadi ezingama-38 eziphambili kunye neehektare ezingama-76,000 zomhlaba kweli lizwe, ithatha iimbovane ngokungxamisekileyo.
I-NTS inamagosa ayi-10 aqeqeshiweyo, ahlola rhoqo, ahlole iindawo zokuhlala aze maxa wambi enze imisebenzi yokunceda abantu.
Le ntlangano iye yaseka indawo yokuqala neyokugcina iimpukane eScotland kwilali yaseThreave eDumfries and Galloway, apho kuhlala khona iintlobo ezisibhozo kwezilishumi zeempukane zaseScotland.
Umphathi weendawo ezinobuhle uDavid Thompson uthi le ndawo ifanelekileyo kwiintsomi.
Wathi: "Ethreave, sinendawo entle yokugcina iimbovane".
"Sinezakhiwo ezindala, imithi emininzi emidala kakhulu kunye nendawo efanelekileyo yokuhlala.
Kodwa zininzi izinto ezingaziwa ngeebhabhathane, yaye ngenxa yoko, umsebenzi esiwenzayo apha nakwezinye iindawo uza kusinceda siqonde ngakumbi oko zifuna ukuze ziphumelele".
Uthe kubalulekile ukuhlolwa kweebhabhathane ngaphambi kokuba kwenziwe imisebenzi yolondolozo, kuba ukonakaliswa okungaqondakaliyo kwendawo yokuhlala kunokubangela ukufa kweebhabhathane ezingama-400 ezifazane kunye neentshontsho zazo, oko kunokubangela ukuba kuphele lonke uluntu lwasekuhlaleni.
Iimpuku ziluhlobo lwesilwanyana ekhuselweyo yaye akukho mthethweni ukubulala, ukuphazamisa okanye ukuphazamisa okanye ukutshabalalisa iindawo ezihlala kuzo.
UElizabeth Ferrell, umongameli waseScotland weBat Conservation Trust, uye wacela abantu ukuba banikele ukuze bancede.
Wathi: "Kusafuneka sifunde okuninzi ngeebhabhathane zethu, yaye kwiintlobo zethu ezininzi, asiyazi into eyenzekayo kwiindidi zazo".
