Iinyikima Neetunami EIndonesia
Abantu abamalunga ne-384 babulawa yinyikima enkulu ne-tsunami eyahlasela isixeko sasePalu eIndonesia ngoLwesihlanu, kutsho amagosa, yaye inani labafileyo kulindeleke ukuba liqhubeke likhula.
Ngenxa yokutshabalala kwezixhobo zonxibelelwano, abasemagunyeni abasenalo ulwazi oluvela kwiDonggala Regency, ummandla osemantla ePalu, okufutshane nendawo yokuzamazama komhlaba okuye kwabangela ukuba kubekho amandla angama-7.5 kwiRichter scale.
Abantu abangaphezu kwe-16 000 baphunyuzwa ePalu emva kwentlekele.
Nazi ezinye zezinto ezibalulekileyo ngePalu neDonggala, kwisiqithi saseCelebes:
IPalu likomkhulu lephondo laseMiddle Celebes kwaye lihlala ekupheleni kwebhayithi encinci kunxweme olusentshona yeCelebes Island, kunye nabemi abaqikelelwa kwi-379,800 ngo-2017.
Esi sixeko sabhiyozela iminyaka engama-40 siphile xa kwabakho itsunami.
I-Donggala yindawo enamabhongo e-Celebes, ehlala ngaphezu kweekhilomitha ezingama-300 kunxweme olusemantla ntshona.
I-regency, indawo yolawulo ephantsi nje kwephondo, yayinabemi abaqikelelweyo abangama-299,200 ngo-2017.
Ukuloba noluntu kunye noluntu loluntu zizinto eziphambili kuqoqosho lwePhondo laseMiddle Celebes, ingakumbi kummandla onxweme lwaseDonggala.
Iimigodi zentsimbi ye-nickel nazo zibalulekile kweli phondo, kodwa zininzi zazo ziseMorowali, kunxweme olungaphaya kweCelebes.
I-Palu neDonggala ziye zachaphazeleka rhoqo ziitsunami kule minyaka ingamakhulu idluleyo, ngokutsho kwe-Indonesia Disaster Management Agency.
Ngowe-1938 i-tsunami yabulala abantu abangaphezu kwe-200 yaza yatshatyalalisa amakhulu emakhaya eDonggala.
Kwakhona, ngo-1996 kwabakho i-tsunami entshona yeDonggala, apho kwafa abantu abasithoba.
I-Indonesia ikwiRing of Fire yasePasifiki yaye ihlala ichaphazeleka ziinyikima.
Nazi ezinye zeenyikima neetsunami eziye zabangela ukuba kubekho ezo ngozi:
Ngo-2004: Inyikima enkulu eyayigubungela unxweme olusentshona wePhondo lase-Indonesia i-Aje eMantla eSumatra ngoDisemba 26, yabangela itsunami eyahlasela amazwe ali-14 yaza yabulala abantu abayi-226.000 kunxweme lwaseIndiya, ngaphezu kwesiqingatha sabo e-Aje.
Ngo-2005: Kwabakho uthotho lweenyikima ezinkulu kunxweme olusentshona yeSumatra ekupheleni kukaMatshi nasekuqaleni kuka-Aprili.
Amakhulu abantu abulawa kwisiqithi saseNias, kunxweme lwaseSumatra.
Ngowama-2006: Inyikima enamandla angama-6.8 kwiRichter's scale yenzeka kumazantsi eJava, eyona nxalenye inabantu abaninzi eIndonesia, yaza yabangela itsunami eyayigubungela unxweme olusemzantsi, yabulala abantu abamalunga nama-700.
Ngo-2009: Inyikima enamandla angama-7.6 yahlasela isixeko sasePadang, ikomkhulu lephondo laseNtshona Sumatra.
Abantu abangaphezu kwe-1 100 babulawa.
Ngo-2010: Inyikima enamandla ka-7.5 kwiRichter's scale yahlasela esinye seziqithi zaseMentawai, kunxweme lwaseSumatra, yaza yabangela itsunami enobude obuziimitha eziyi-10 eyatshabalalisa amashumi amawaka eedolophana yaza yabulala abantu abamalunga nama-300.
Ngo-2016: Inyikima enzulu yahlasela urhulumente wasePidi eAtjeh yaza yabangela umonakalo nokothuka, njengoko abantu bakhunjuzwa ngomonakalo owabangelwa yinyikima ne-tsunami ka-2004.
Kwakungekho tsunami ngeli xesha kodwa abantu abangaphezu kwekhulu bafa ngenxa yokudumba kwezakhiwo.
Ngo-2018: Iinyikima ezininzi zenzeka kwisiqithi seLombok, isiqithi seendwendwe zaseIndonesia, apho kwafa abantu abangaphezu kwe-500, uninzi lwazo lusemantla esi siqithi.
Le nyikima yatshayela amawaka ezakhiwo yaza yabangela ukuba amawaka abakhenkethi abambalwa balahlekelwe yindawo yokulala.
Unyana omdala kaSarah Palin ubanjwe etyholwa ngokwenzakalisa amalungu entsapho
UTrac Palin, oyena nyana mkhulu kaSarah Palin, owayesakuba nguRhuluneli waseAlaska, nomntu oza kuba nguSekela-Mongameli, ubanjwe etyholwa ngokwenzakalisa amakhaya.
UPalin, 29, waseWasilla, eAlaska, wabanjwa etyholwa ngokurhwaphiliza amabhodlo asekhaya, ukuphazamisa ingxelo engqongqo kwikhaya lakhe, nokumelana naye xa etyholwa, ngokutsho kwengxelo ekhutshwe ngoMgqibelo ngamaTroopers aseAlaska State.
Ngokwengxelo yamapolisa, xa umntu awayenomdla kuye wazama ukubiza amapolisa ukuze abike ngokuqhankqalaza kwakhe, wayithabatha ifowuni yakhe.
UPalin ugcinwa kwiNtolongo yaseMat-Su eneengqekembe ezingama-$500, ingxelo ye-KTUU.
Lo mntu wavela enkundleni ngoMgqibelo, esithi 'uyatshata, ngokuqinisekileyo' xa ebuzwa oku, inethiwekhi yaxela.
UPalin utyholwa ngokuxhatshazwa kwetyala lesithathu, elibhekisela kumbandela wokufumana isigwebo esifikelela kunyaka omnye entolongweni kunye nehlawulo elifikelela kwi-250,000 yeedola.
Kwakhona umtyholwa ngokwenza into ephosakeleyo, ekwafuneka ayenze, enokufumana isigwebo sentolongo esisodwa ne-$2,000.
Akusiyo into yokuqala ukuba uPalin athethelelwe ngobugwenxa.
NgoDisemba 2017 watyholwa ngokuxhaphaza uyise, uTodd Palin.
Umama wakhe uSarah Palin wabiza amapolisa ukuze abike ngokuxhatshazwa.
Eli tyala ngoku lisebenza kwiNkundla yamaNcedisi aseAlaska.
NgoJanuwari 2016, watyholwa ngokudlwengula ekhaya, ukuphazamisa ingxelo yobundlobongela basekhaya kunye nokuba nesibhamu esithelekiswa nesiganeko.
Umhlobo wakhe wathi wambetha ebusweni.
USarah Palin wagxekwa liqela lamajoni asele ekhonza e-Iraq ngo-2016 emva kokunxibelelana nokuziphatha konogonyamelo konyana wakhe kwi-PTSD, ekuthiwa wayeza kuqhubeka nokuyenza ngexesha lakhe elisebenza e-Iraq.
