Abamangali baseburhulumenteni bafuna isigwebo sokufa esinqabileyo kumntu osolwayo kwingozi yobugebenga kwisiXeko saseNew York
Abamangali baseburhulumenteni eNew York bafuna isigwebo sokufa sikaSajfoello Sajpov, osolwayo kwi-terrorism eNew York City, apho kwabulawa abantu abasibhozo, isigwebo esinqabileyo esingazange senziwe kweli lizwe ukususela ngo-1953.
USajpov, 30, uthi wasebenzisa itruck eyayiharhwa yiHome Depot ukuze enze umlo kumzila webhayisekile kwiWest Side Highway eseLower Manhattan, apho wagqusha khona abahambi ngeenyawo nabamabhayisekile ababeza kumngena ngo-Oktobha.
Ukuze kuqinisekiswe ukuba isigwebo sokufa sifanelekile, abamangali baya kufuneka babonise ukuba uSajpov 'wabulala ngamabomu' la maxhoba asibhozo waza 'wawenzakalisa' umzimba wakhe, ngokutsho kwesibhengezo senjongo esifuna ukufa, esifakwe kwiSithili saseNew York esiseMzantsi.
Kwezi zityholo zimbini, isigwebo sokufa sinokwenzeka, ngokutsho kwexwebhu eliye laziswa enkundleni.
Kwiiveki emva kokuhlaselwa, iJaji enkulu yaseFederal yavuma ukuba kuthiwe kukho amatyala angama-22, kuquka amatyala asibhozo okubulala ngenjongo yokuqhatha, ityala eliqhelekileyo elisetyenziswa ngabasemagunyeni kwiinkundla zamatyala ukuze kuchaswe ulwaphulo-mthetho oluhleliweyo, netyala lobundlobongela nokutshatyalaliswa kweemoto.
Ababheno bathi lo mlo wawufuna "ukucwangciswa nokucwangciswa okunzulu", yaye bathi indlela uSajpov awawenza ngayo lo mlo "yayinkqayi, inkohlakalo, yaye inkohlakalo".
"USajfoello Habiboellayevich Sajpov wenzakalisa, wonakalisa, wabulala iintsapho nabahlobo bakaDiego Enrique Angelini, uNicolas Cleves, uAnn-Laure Decadt, uDarren Drake, uAriel Erlij, uHernan Ferruchi, uHernan Diego Mendoza noAlejandro Damian Pagnucco", itsho njalo ingxelo.
Amaxhoba amahlanu ayeziindwendwe zaseArgentina.
Kwiminyaka engaphezu kweshumi eyadlulayo, kwavela ityala elalifuna isigwebo sokufa kwiSithili saseNew York.
Umtyholwa, uKhalid Barnes, wagwetywa ngokubulala abathengisi ababini beziyobisi kodwa wagwetywa ubomi bakhe bonke ngoSeptemba 2009.
Isigwebo sokufa sigqitywe ukubulawa kwicala likaRhulumente eNew York ngowe-1953 ngoJulius noEthel Rosenberg, isibini esabulawa emva kokuba sigwetywe iminyaka emibini ngaphambili ngenxa yokungcatsha iUSSR ngexesha leMfazwe Yomlomo.
Bobabini oonyana bakaRosenberg babulawa ngombane ngoJuni 19, 1953.
Ngokutsho kwamaxwebhu enkundla, uSajpov, ovela eUzbekistan, akazange abonise ukuzisola kwiintsuku okanye kwiinyanga emva kokuhlaselwa.
Wazisa amapolisa ukuba wayeziva ekhululekile ngenxa yoko wakwenzayo.
USajpov uxelele abasemagunyeni ukuba waphefumlelwa ukuba enze lo mlo emva kokubukela iividiyo ze-ISIS kwifowuni yakhe, ngokutsho kwesityholo.
Kwakhona wacela ukuba ibhanti ye-ISIS ibekwe egumbini lakhe esibhedlele, kwaxelelwa amapolisa.
Wavuma ukuba akanatyala kwizityholo ezingama-22.
UDavid Patton, omnye wabameli bakarhulumente bamazwe aseburhulumenteni abamele uSajpov, wathi 'udimazekile ngokwemvelo' ngesigqibo sommangaleli.
UPatton wathi: "Sicinga ukuba isigqibo sokunyanzelisa ukufa kunokuba samkele isigwebo sokubandezeleka ubomi babo bonke ngaphandle kokukhululwa siya kulandisa intlungu ebangelwa zezi ziganeko kubo bonke ababandakanyekileyo".
Ukhuselo lukaSajpov lwalukhe lwabongoza abamangali ukuba bangayifuni loo nto.
ILungu lePalamente eliGqwesileyo lithi uNigel FARAGE ufanele akhokele iingxoxo zeBrexit
UNigel Farage uthembise 'ukuqokelela umkhosi wabantu' namhlanje xa wayechasa intlanganiso yeConservative Party.
Owayesakuba yinkokeli ye-Ukip wathi abezopolitiko kufuneka 'bazive ubushushu' bama-euro-sceptics, ngoxa omnye wepalamente kaTheresa May wacebisa ukuba amnike igunya lokulawula iingxoxo ne-EU.
Umlindi ongumnqweno uPeter Bone waxelela abameli bematheko eBirmingham ukuba i-UK 'yayisele iza kuba sephandle' ukuba uMnu Farage wayeyinkokeli ye-Brexit.
Kodwa umngeni uMay awujongene nawo ekubuyiseni amaqela ahlukeneyo, ugxininiswa ngamaqela amabini agqwesileyo asekela iRemain, athatha inxaxheba kwintlanganiso eyahlukileyo yokuchasa iBrexit kwisixeko.
UMongameli ufumana kunzima ukugcina isithembiso sakhe seChequers sihleli njengoko sihlaselwa ngabakhweli beBrexit, abemi beRemainers kunye ne-EU.
Abahlali bathi uza kuqhubeka uzama ukwenza isivumelwano neBrussels phezu kwayo nje imiphumo, ngaloo ndlela enyanzelise ama-Eurosceptics namaLebour ukuba akhethe phakathi kwepakethe yakhe 'nentlekele'.
UBone wathi kwintlanganiso yeLeave Means Leave eSolihull "ufuna ukulahla iChequers kwinto engcolileyo".
Wacebisa ukuba uFarage axoxwe aze athathwe uxanduva lokuthengiselana neBrussels.
UBone wathi: "Ukuba wayegqibezele inkonzo, ngoku besingayi kuphinda sihlangane nayo".
Eli lungu laseWellingborough laongeza lathi: "Ndiza kuxhasa iBrexit, kodwa kufuneka silahle iChequers kwinto engcolileyo".
Ecacisa indlela awayekhetha ngayo ukuchasana ne-EU, wathi: "Asizange silwe kwiimfazwe ezimbini zehlabathi ukuze sibe phantsi.
Sifuna ukwenza imithetho yethu kwilizwe lethu".
UBone ubonisa ukuba uluvo loluntu lutshintshile ukususela kwi-referendum ka-2016: "Ingcamango yokuba abantu base-UK batshintshile kwaye bafuna ukuhlala kwi-EU ayinyani ngokupheleleyo".
Umongameli weBrexit ogcina izithethe, uAndrea Jenkyns, naye wathatha inxaxheba kulo msitho, wathi kumajelo eendaba: "Ndiye ndithi nje: ndunankulu, phulaphula abantu.
I-Chequers ayithandwa ngabantu ngokubanzi, abachasi abafuni ukuvota, ayithandwa kwiqela lethu nakubashumayeli bethu abahamba emnyango nomnyango ukuze sifumane ukhetho.
"Yenza iChequers iwele phantsi uze uphulaphule".
Kwisibhengezo sakhe kuMay, wongezelela wathi: "Ootitshala-mali bayayigcina imisebenzi yabo xa behlala bethembekile kwizithembiso zabo".
UFarage waxelela intlanganiso ukuba oopolitiko kufuneka 'bazive zishushu' xa befuna ukubonisa isigqibo esenziwe kwi Referendum ka-2016.
Wathi: "Ngoku ngumcimbi wokuthembana phakathi kwethu, abantu, kunye nesigaba sethu sezepolitiki".
"Bazama ukukhanyela iBrexit, kwaye sihlangene namhlanje ukuze sibabalisele ukuba 'asiyi kunivumela niphume kule nto.'"
Kwibhokisi yakhe eya kumaqela amaninzi, wongezelela wathi: "Ndifuna nilahle umlilo kwiklasi yethu yezopolitiko, esondele ekuthengiseni iBrexit.
Siyayixhobisa imikhosi yabantu beli lizwe esasinika uloyiso kwi Referendum yeBrexit kwaye asiyi kuphumla de sibe yiUnited Kingdom ezimeleyo, ezizimeleyo neziqhayisayo kwakhona".
Okwangoku, amaRemainers ahamba eBirmingham, equkumbela lo msitho ngomsitho weeyure ezimbini kumbindi wesixeko.
