Iingcamango zokuvula imfazwe yorhwebo phakathi kweUnited States neTshayina zazinqabile, yaye nangona imfazwe ingekaqalwanga, iingcali zithi umsantsa phakathi kwamazwe omabini unokuba luncedo kwiPeking kwixesha elide.
US President Donald Trump, wanikela isilumkiso sokuqala ekuqaleni konyaka ngokunyusa irhafu kwimveliso ebalulekileyo yaseTshayina ethunyelwa kwamanye amazwe, kuquka iipaneli zelanga, intsimbi nealuminium.
Eyona ngxaki ibalulekileyo yabonakaliswa kule veki xa kwachazwa amaxabiso amatsha anempembelelo, anyuswe irhafu kwiimveliso ezingama-200 ezigidi zeedola (i-150 ezigidi ze-euro), isiqingatha sezinto eziphuma e-China ziza e-US.
I-Beijing iye yaziphindezela, kutshanje, ngokunyusa amaxabiso e-US $ 60 billion kwiimveliso zase-US ukusuka kwi-5 ukuya kwi-10%.
I-China ithembise ukuba iza kulinganisa i-US ngalo lonke ixesha, yaye ihlabathi elinesibini ngobukhulu kwezoqoqosho liza kuba liza kuqhubeka lingakhange libanjwe ngokukhawuleza.
Ukuze iWashington iqubude, izicelo kufuneka zenziwe, kodwa ukuqubuda esidlangalaleni e-US kubuhlungu kakhulu kuMongameli waseTshayina uXi Jinping.
Noko ke, iingcali zithi ukuba iBeijing yenza ngobulumko, imfazwe yorhwebo neUnited States inokuxhasa iChina kwixesha elide, kuba ukuxhomekeka kwezoqoqosho zomibini kuya kuncipha.
"Ukuthi isigqibo esikhawulezayo kwezopolitiko eWashington okanye eBeijing sinokudala iimeko ezinokubangela ukuba elinye lamazwe liwele kwicala lokukhululeka kwezoqoqosho, eneneni, liyingozi ngakumbi kunokuba ababukeli babesazi ngaphambili", utshilo uAbigail Grace, ophanda kwiZiko Lokhuseleko Olutsha LwaseMerika, iqela elicebisa ngeendaba zokhuseleko lwesizwe, elijolise eAsia.
