IYurophu yafumana isihloko xa iqela likayise waseDenmark uThomas Bjorn lafumana amanqaku ayi-14.5 ukuze litshabalalise iUnited States.
Inkwenkwezi yeqela laseMerika, uPhil Mickelson, owayenzima phantse yonke le nkundla, wavumela umbetho wakhe omde ukusuka kwi-tee ukuba ufikelele kwipar 3, umngxuma 16, waza wavuma ukulahlekelwa nguFrancesco Molinari.
Umdlali wegalufa waseItali, uMolinari, wakhazimla kuwo onke amaqela akhe, waba ngomnye wabadlali abane abakha bafumana i-5-0-0 ukususela oko lo mdlalo waqalisa ngo-1979.
UJordan Spieth waseMerika wagxothwa ngumdlali ophakamileyo kwiqela laseYurophu, uThorbjorn Olesen waseDenmark, edlala ngemingxuma emihlanu nangemingxuma emine.
Umdlali ophezulu kakhulu kwibala lehlabathi, uDustin Johnson, walahlekelwa ziimbobo ezi-2 phantsi kweyodwa kwiimbambo ze-Ian Poulter wase-UK, owayedlala umdlalo wakhe wokugqibela kwi-Ryder Cup.
USegrio Garcia waseSpain, ongumakadebona owathabatha iRyder Cup ezisibhozo, waba ngoyena mdlali uphambili eYurophu kuwo onke amatumente akhe abonwa nge-25.5 kwimidlalo yakhe.
"Andizange ndikhawuleze ndilile, kodwa namhlanje andinakukwazi ukuyitshintsha.
Kube ngunyaka onzima.
Ndiyambulela kakhulu uTomas ngokundinyula nokundikholelwa.
Ndivuya gqitha kuba sifumene indebe kwakhona.
Oku kungenxa yeqela, yaye ndiyavuya ndakwazi ukunceda,' watsho uGarcia, owayechukumisekile emva koqoqosho lwaseYurophu.
Uyadlulisela elo tyala kumntu wakhe, uJohn Ram, owathi ngoLwesine wayidlula intsomi yaseMerika uTiger Woods ngemingxunya emibini nangemingxunya emibini kumdlalo weqonga.
"Ibhongo elikhulu endilivayo ngokutshabalalisa uTiger Woods, kuba ndandimlandela lo mfana ndisakhula", utsho uRahm oneminyaka eyi-23.
UWoods uphulukene nayo yonke imidlalo emine eFransi, kwaye ngoku unerekhodi ye-13-21-3 kwiNdebe yeRyder.
Ingxelo engaqhelekanga evela komnye wabadlali abakhulu behlabathi, ophumelele iimbasa ezili-14, eyesibini kuphela emva kukaJack Nicklaus.
Iqela laseMerika lalisokola ukufumana i-fairways kule mpelaveki, ngaphandle kukaPatrick Reed, uJustin Thomas noTony Finau, abadlala kwinqanaba eliphezulu kulo lonke itumente.
