Ngethuba nje elifutshane namhlanje, siye sayenza yaba nzima ngakumbi iYurophu.
Sazama ukumelana nabo.
Nokuba yintoni na, ndiyakuhlonela uThomas.
Ungumphathi omkhulu.
Bonke abadlali abali-12 beqela lakhe babedlala kakuhle.
Siza kuhlanganisana kwakhona, kwaye ndiza kusebenza ne-PGA yaseMerika kunye neKomiti yethu ye-Ryder Cup kwaye sijonge phambili.
