Ukuhlaziywa kweGlood Glow: Ukuxinana kuyaphela kwiphondo lasePinellas, Manatee naseSarasota
Ingxelo yakutshanje yeFlorida Fish and Wildlife Conservation Commission ibonisa ukuba inani le-Red Claw liye lehla ngokubanzi kwiindawo ezikufutshane neTampa Bay Area (ekunxweme olusentshona yeFlorida, eUnited States).
Ngokutsho kwale komiti, kukho iingxelo zokunyuka ngokuthe ngcembe kwe-Red Bulb kwiphondo lasePinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte naseCollier, nto leyo enokubonisa ukwehla kwamaqondo.
Umlambo iRed Glove unqumla umgama oziikhilomitha ezingama-200 ukusuka kumantla ePinellas ukuya kumazantsi eLee Counties.
Kukho iindawo ezinokuba ziindawo ezimalunga neekhilomitha ezili-16 kunxweme lwaseHillsborough County, kodwa zingaphantsi kwezo zabonwa kwiveki ephelileyo.
Kwakhona, kuye kwabonwa ukukhanya okubomvu kwiPhondo lasePasco.
Kukho iingxelo ezinobukhulu obuphakathi kunxweme lwePinellas County kwiveki ephelileyo, iingxelo ezincinci ukuya phezulu kunxweme lweHillsborough County, iingxelo ezincinci ukuya phezulu kwiManatee County, iingxelo ezincinci ukuya phezulu kunxweme lweSarasota County, iingxelo ezincinci ukuya phezulu kwiCharlotte County, iingxelo ezincinci ukuya phezulu kunxweme lweLee County, kunye neengxelo ezincinci kwiCollier County.
Kukho iingxelo eziqhubekayo zokuba kukho ukuphazamiseka kwendlela yomoya kwiphondo lasePinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee naseCollier.
Kumntla-ntshona weFlorida, akukho ngxelo yokugxekwa komoya kwiveki ephelileyo.
